This paper is primarily focused on testing the performance of Deep Neural Network (DNN) models, which falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the efficiency of testing, which is related to Software Engineering (cs.SE). The use of DNNs also falls under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) categories. Finally, the paper discusses the use of probability distributions and sampling, which is related to Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
